  <description><![CDATA[<p>We are delighted to feature this wonderful hotel for the first time. Located on the shore of Lake Geneva with beautiful views, it is in an enviable position. It is opposite the boat stop for easy access to trips on the lake and only a few minutes’ walk from the centre of Evian. The rooms are all very spacious with views overlooking either the lake or the resort/mountains. There is a large outdoor swimming pool and an impressive ‘Buddha-bar’ spa, with indoor pool, which is open all day for residents only. Children are well catered for with a free kids club each afternoon during the French school holidays and a play room.</p>]]></description>
