  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>The standard double or twin bedrooms are very spacious with a lounge area, bath, satellite TV, tea &amp; coffee making facilities, safe, minibar and a view overlooking the resort.</li>
<li>The Deluxe bedrooms are the same size, with an additional shower and balcony overlooking the lake.</li>
<li>Free spa access is included while staying in a Deluxe room.</li>
<li>Both rooms can take an additional bed and children up to 12 stay free. Interconnecting rooms are available</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
